lma / listmacro               Lists macros
 
   Format:
      ;lma
               Lists all macros belonging to current profiles
      ;lma -w
               Lists all macros associated with the current world 
      ;lma -g
               Lists all macros associated with the current guild
      ;lma -r
               Lists all macros associated with the current race
      ;lma -c
               Lists all macros associated with the current character
      ;lma -x <category>
               Lists all macros belonging to the current custom profile derived
                  from the category (template) <category>
      ;lma -d <prof>
               Lists all macros belonging to the profile <prof>
      ;lma -i
               Lists all active macro interfaces

   User commands:
      lma / listma / listmacro
